-- Ambac to announce a capital infusion: source
-- 
-- Wed Mar 5, 2008 12:50pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/03/05/us-bonds-insurers-ambac-infusion-idUSWEN434820080305

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Ambac Financial Group Inc plans to soon announce a capital infusion, a person briefed on the matter said on Wednesday. 

 Further details were not immediately available. An Ambac spokesman was not immediately available for comment. (Reporting by  Dan Wilchins ; Editing by  Derek Caney )